"Tap here to select multiple cutlings, reorder them, or restore recently deleted ones." = "Ketik di sini untuk memilih beberapa cutling, menyusunnya semula, atau memulihkan yang baru dipadam.";
"Long-press a cutling" = "Tekan lama pada cutling";
"Hold any card for quick actions: copy, edit, share, or delete." = "Tahan mana-mana kad untuk tindakan pantas: salin, edit, kongsi, atau padam.";
"Drag to select" = "Seret untuk memilih";
"Swipe across cards to select a range. Swipe back over them to deselect." = "Leret merentasi kad untuk memilih julat. Leret semula ke atasnya untuk membatalkan pilihan.";
"Smart field matching" = "Padanan medan pintar";
"Cutling spots email, URL, phone, and address fields, then floats matching snippets to the top of the keyboard." = "Cutling mengesan medan e-mel, URL, telefon dan alamat, kemudian memaparkan snipet yang sepadan di bahagian atas papan kekunci.";
"Create a new cutling" = "Cipta Cutling baharu";
"Save text or image snippets you'll reuse from any app." = "Simpan petikan teks atau imej yang akan anda guna semula dari mana-mana aplikasi.";

/* MARK: - Welcome Window (macOS first launch) */
"Welcome to Cutling" = "Selamat Datang ke Cutling";
"Your clipboard, organised." = "Papan keratan anda, tersusun rapi.";
"Save the snippets, images, and links you reuse. Capture everything you copy. Paste anywhere with one shortcut." = "Simpan petikan, imej dan pautan yang anda guna semula. Tangkap semua yang anda salin. Tampal di mana-mana dengan satu pintasan.";
"Look up. Cutling lives in your menu bar" = "Lihat ke atas. Cutling berada di bar menu anda";
"The clipboard icon at the top of your screen opens Cutling any time. Click it to see your saved cutlings and recent clipboard history." = "Ikon papan keratan di bahagian atas skrin anda membuka Cutling bila-bila masa. Klik untuk melihat cutling yang tersimpan dan sejarah papan keratan terkini.";
"Summon Cutling from anywhere" = "Panggil Cutling dari mana-mana";
"Press ⌘⇧V from any app to open a floating picker at your cursor. Pick a cutling and it's ready to paste, no menu bar trip required." = "Tekan ⌘⇧V dari mana-mana app untuk membuka pemilih terapung di kursor anda. Pilih satu cutling dan ia sedia untuk ditampal, tanpa perlu ke bar menu.";
"Rebind it later in Settings → Hotkey." = "Anda boleh menukar pintasan kemudian di Tetapan → Pintasan.";
"Almost there" = "Hampir siap";
"You're all set" = "Semuanya sedia";
"Two quick permissions so Cutling can work the way you'd expect. You can change either later in Settings." = "Dua kebenaran ringkas supaya Cutling boleh berfungsi seperti yang anda jangkakan. Anda boleh menukar mana-mana satu kemudian dalam Tetapan.";
"Launch at login" = "Lancar semasa log masuk";
"Open Cutling automatically when you sign in." = "Buka Cutling secara automatik apabila anda log masuk.";
"Accessibility access" = "Akses Kebolehcapaian";
"Granted. Cutling can paste directly into other apps." = "Diberikan. Cutling boleh menampal terus ke dalam app lain.";
"Lets Cutling paste a cutling straight into the app you were using." = "Membenarkan Cutling menampal cutling terus ke dalam app yang sedang anda gunakan.";
"Grant" = "Berikan";
"You can skip Accessibility and grant it later from Settings → Paste." = "Anda boleh melangkau Kebolehcapaian dan memberikannya kemudian dari Tetapan → Tampal.";
